description:
This is a 15 minute workout called 'Quick But Brutal HIIT | 15 Minute Indoor Cycling Workout' from the channel GCN Training.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT and Cardio/Indoor biking.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Manon is joined by Katie, Maddie, Caer, and Morgan for a short, sweet 15-minute workout! After a warm up manon will take us through intervals of all-out efforts and rests. This a great session for when you're short on time but want to get your sweat on! ðŸ¥µ
